title: Rename core diversity functions
body:
This pull request is designed to fix #1 by renaming all of the core diversity functions:
- alpha(), beta(), rho(), gamma() with raw.alpha(), etc.
- alphabar(), betabar(), etc. with normalised.alpha(), etc.
- sub/supercommunity.alpha() with raw.sub/supercommunity.alpha(), etc.
- sub/supercommunity.alpha.bar() with normalised.sub/supercommunity.alpha(), etc.
  Except sub/supercommunity.gamma() which I have left as is for now since they are not really raw or normalised.
